The FCC ID for this device covers both the [[TRENDnet TEW-713RE]] and the [[TRENDnet TEW-714TRU]].
"7018N-A107-03" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos. <!-- I don't know the manufacturer, but certainly semanticizing all of the board text on this site would provide elucidation. -->
Default settings are per the FCC manual.
The default SSID for this device is probably '''TRENDnet713''', which would be shared with the [[TRENDnet TEW-713BR]], though, the 713BR would seem to have never been released. This is *not* the SSID noted in the manual (which, instead, is '''TRENDnet733_2.4GHz_XXXX''', used by the [[TRENDnet TEW-733GR]]), but it would fit with TRENDnet's naming scheme. This SSID is found in WiGLE data spanning from (mostly, but one late 2013) 2014 - 2019, which matches fairly closely with the release of this device.
The OUI in this entry is sourced from a marketplace (eBay) label.
